Summary: Very bright orange object travelling fast across sky
divs: Sighting Details1. Outside walking dogs 2. The brightness of the object, brighter then any star and going fast 3. Weather balloon, satellite 4. Skeptical, but wanting to believe. 6. Went inside to grab parents, object gone 48 second video recorded.
